#  BATTLE-TESTED COMMANDER under the hood (per upstream readme:
#  "Uses battle-tested Commander package under the hood") but
#  hides Commander behind a Next.js-style developer experience.
#  Used by tamagui/tamagui (Tamagui cross-platform UI 12k+
